---
import PageHeading from "../components/page-heading.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="DMCA - Bangla Web Fonts">
  <section class="relative z-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">
    <PageHeading
      title="DMCA"
      description="Last updated: 15 March 2025"
    />

<p class="mt-4">
      <strong>Bangla Web Fonts</strong> only hosts fonts that are licensed for public use, redistribution, and embedding. Most of the fonts available on this site are licensed under:
    </p>
    
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-4 space-y-1">
      <li><span class="font-medium">SIL Open Font License (OFL)</span></li>
      <li><span class="font-medium">GNU GPL with the Font Exception</span></li>
      <li><span class="font-medium">Custom open licenses</span> from the original font creators, often labeled as <span class="italic">"উন্মুক্ত"</span> (open) in the font metadata or official release pages</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-4">
      We take care to verify license information from the font’s metadata and the original creator's website before hosting.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4">
      If you believe a font has been included in error, or that it infringes your copyright, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:contact.shihab1246@gmail.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">contact.shihab1246@gmail.com</a>
    </p>

    

  </section>
</Layout>